</comment>
                            <comment id="12433458" author="skambha" created="Fri, 8 Sep 2006 18:43:56 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;This fix was merged to 10.2 as part of the mega merge: &lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/viewvc?view=rev&amp;amp;revision=441540&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/viewvc?view=rev&amp;amp;revision=441540&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

